# Orator C++/CUDA formatting — machine-enforced realization of the
# Constitution Article V/VII style: Google C++ Style, 2-space indent,
# pointer-left, 80 columns. Applied to .cc/.cu/.h/.cuh.
---
Language: Cpp
BasedOnStyle: Google
IndentWidth: 2
ColumnLimit: 80
PointerAlignment: Left
DerivePointerAlignment: false
AccessModifierOffset: -1
IncludeBlocks: Preserve
SortIncludes: false
...
